  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to do a descriptive analysis of the cutaneous toxicity observed in
      patients treated using targeted therapies in order to have a better understanding of the skin
      pathophysiology.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
